<item>
            <title>[CASSANDRA-17131] Fix formatting in  cassandra.yaml</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-17131</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;We have a few parameters with small formatting issues in cassandra.yaml which are not caught because by default they are commented out.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Cassandra 4.0:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;a few parameters are added with &lt;em&gt;parameter &lt;b&gt;=&lt;/b&gt; value&lt;/em&gt; instead of &lt;em&gt;parameter &lt;b&gt;:&lt;/b&gt; value&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;p&gt;trunk:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;same issue as in 4.0&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;few parameters added with &lt;em&gt;;&lt;/em&gt; after the value&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
