                            <comment id="17441366" author="edimitrova" created="Tue, 9 Nov 2021 21:21:26 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I already opened a follow up ticket for &lt;em&gt;internode_application_timeout_in_ms -&lt;/em&gt;&#160;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-17132&quot; title=&quot;Fix startup issue with internode_application_timeout_in_ms&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CASSANDRA-17132&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CASSANDRA-17132&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

